were made at the IOC accredited laboratory "Australian Government
Analytical Laboratories", the FINA press release said.
</P>
<P>
The FINA Executive in their meeting held on Wednesday, has
decided according to FINA Rule DC 8.3 to provisionally suspend the
four Chinese swimmers, without hearing, until a hearing can be
made following the test of the B sample, the press release
said. 
