serious nature of its open-door promise by continuing intensified
dialogues with those countries interested in the eastward
expansion of the western military alliance.
</P>
<P>
NATO has promised to remain open to further eastward expansion,
but there is no decision on any of the countries for the second
wave of the expansion. NATO is expected to review the issue at
its Washington Summit in the spring of 1999. 
