enhance relations between the two brotherly countries, according
to the sources.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, Sharif is also scheduled to have a separate meeting
with Indian Prime Minister Inder Kumar Gujral during the summit to
discuss the possibility of resuming the foreign secretary level
talks between Pakistan and India, the sources said.
</P>
<P>
Pakistan and India agreed to form working groups to discuss all
outstanding issues between the two countries at their foreign
secretary level meeting held in June last year in Islamabad, but
the agreement has yet to be operationalized, the sources said.
