tariffs on Israeli imports. Meanwhile, he added, the ban will also
be justified by the devaluation of Indonesia's currency by 70
percent in the past weeks.
</P>
<P>
BEIRUT -- Lebanese Arch Financial Group has announced the
purchase of a 76 percent stake in al-Mughtareb, a small Beirut
bank valued at 14 million U.S. dollars, Beirut Times reported
Tuesday.
</P>
