interbank money market dropped nearly 30 percent to 414.9 billion
yuan (about 50 billion US dollars) in 1997, according to official
statistics.
</P>
<P>
The amount represents a daily trading volume of 1.64 billion
yuan for the 253 trading sessions last year.
</P>
<P>
